com.epoch.evals

Class EvalResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.evals.EvalResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FormatConstants, EvalResultConstants, GradeConstants

    public class EvalResult
extends Object
implements FormatConstants, EvalResultConstants, GradeConstants
    Holds a response, and usually the result of its evaluation. Also holds information about the instantiation of a student's view of a question:
    • In multiple-choice, fillblank, and rank questions, lastResponse contains the order of the options presented to the student.
    Even when a student has not yet responded, lastResponse may be populated with the instantiation information. In the database table corresponding to the EvalResult class, this information is recorded as the 0th response.
